race.description: Keep Them Super With Supercoat Handicap (C2)
race.comment: VORKUTA (6) got the job done over this course and distance last time out and winning rider Lerena sticks in the saddle. Maps ideally for this from gate three and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. EFFIE'S JOY (14) finally broke the maiden status at the latest effort and will have derived a bunch of confidence from that overdue victory. Can go right on with it now. LEXY ROSE (11) resumes here but the form she showed when last in work was good enough for a race like this. Keep very safe. The well-related MONARCH EXPRESS (8) (half to G3 winner and G2 placed Mirette) is a last-start winner who is usually thereabouts. In the mix for some minor money. KIRORO PEAK (2) is a stayer resuming who should be hitting the line with gusto.
